wholeText.mainContentText: 4 NIGHT Hsien means a general in Taiwanese language and is the last name. So, means general Fan. In Jia Jiang’s group, they always work in a pair. Fan Jiang Jun always works with Hsien Jiang Jun 2 DAY “將 軍” means a general in Taiwanese language and “謝”（“Hsein”）is the last name. So, “謝 將 軍“ means “general Fan”. In Jia Jiang’s group, they always work in a pair.4
